parameters.name: MaxResults
parameters.description:
The number of entries to return on each page. Maximum value: 100.

Default value:

*   If you do not configure this parameter or if you set this parameter to a value less than 20, the default value is 20.
*   If you set this parameter to a value that is greater than 100, the default value is 100.

parameters.name: NetTestType
parameters.description: The type of the network test.

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description: The token that determines the start position of the query. Set this parameter to the value of the NextToken parameter that is returned from the last call.
